<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>댕냥이 분양센터</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}

body{
  background:#f5f6fa;
  font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;
}

header{
  background:#ffcc4d;
  padding:30px 20px;
  text-align:center;
  box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

header h1{
  font-size:32px;
}

header p{
  margin-top:10px;
  color:#555;
}

.menu{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:15px;
  margin-top:20px;
}

.menu a{
  text-decoration:none;
  background:white;
  color:#333;
  padding:10px 15px;
  border-radius:10px;
  font-weight:bold;
}

.container{
  width:95%;
  max-width:1200px;
  margin:30px auto;
}

.notice{
  background:#fff7a8;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:12px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.notice h2{
  font-size:18px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

.board{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
  gap:20px;
}

.card{
  background:#fff7a8;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:12px;
  position:relative;
  min-height:200px;
  box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.pin{
  position:absolute;
  top:-8px;
  left:50%;
  transform:translateX(-50%);
  font-size:24px;
}

.card h3{
  margin-top:10px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card p{
  margin-bottom:8px;
  font-size:14px;
}

.footer{
  margin-top:50px;
  padding:20px;
  text-align:center;
  background:#fff;
  color:#666;
}

.search{
  margin:20px 0;
}

.search input{
  width:100%;
  padding:12px;
  border-radius:10px;
  border:1px solid #ccc;
}

.badge{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:4px 8px;
  border-radius:8px;
  background:#fff;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}

.dog{background:#d8f3ff;}
.cat{background:#ffd8ef;}

@media(max-width:700px){
  header h1{
    font-size:24px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>🐶🐱 댕냥이 분양센터</h1>
  <p>건강한 반려동물의 새로운 가족을 찾아드립니다</p>

  <div class="menu">
    <a href="#">강아지</a>
    <a href="#">고양이</a>
    <a href="#">분양문의</a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="notice">
    <h2>📢 공지사항</h2>
    <p>분양 문의는 카카오톡 또는 오픈채팅 링크를 이용해주세요.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="search">
    <input type="text" placeholder="품종 검색">
  </div>

  <div class="board">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="pin">📌</div>
      <span class="badge dog">강아지</span>
      <h3>말티푸</h3>
      <p>성별 : 여아</p>
      <p>접종 완료</p>
      <p>2개월</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="pin">📌</div>
      <span class="badge cat">고양이</span>
      <h3>실버뱅갈</h3>
      <p>성별 : 남아</p>
      <p>건강검진 완료</p>
      <p>3개월</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="pin">📌</div>
      <span class="badge dog">강아지</span>
      <h3>포메라니안</h3>
      <p>성별 : 남아</p>
      <p>접종 완료</p>
      <p>2개월</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
  © 2026 댕냥이 분양센터
</div>

</body>
</html>
